data.description: Introducing a charming two-story home nestled in the desirable Lindsey Place community. This spacious residence boasts 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. With a prime location, this property offers not only a place to call home but also a lifestyle enriched by convenience and nearby amenities. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a well-designed layout that includes two distinct living areas. These versatile spaces offer endless possibilities, whether you're looking to entertain guests, create a cozy family room, or set up a home office. Upstairs, you'll discover the comfortable sleeping quarters. Four generously sized bedrooms offer both privacy and comfort, making this home ideal for families or those who desire extra space for guests, hobbies, or a home gym. The primary bedroom includes an en-suite bathroom, ensuring a peaceful retreat after a long day. Situated in the sought-after Lindsey Place neighborhood, this home offers more than just comfort-it offers a prime location. With an array of nearby restaurants and shopping options, your everyday needs are easily met. For family-friendly entertainment, Six Flags and educational opportunities at UTSA are just a short drive away, making weekends full of adventure and learning. Imagine living in a home where every convenience is within reach, from daily essentials to leisure activities. Don't miss your chance to own this fantastic property in Lindsey Place.
